{"tid":957334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神婆來年預言】保國「盲婆」預測特朗普因病致聾 指亞洲有大海嘯中日當災","createTime":"2018-12-27T02:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T21:56:08.000Z","uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"20f501bc5d6b44d54e4c108af3f4b6c5d65690d4","tid":957334,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181227&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59073575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181227%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59073575&d=wHbHYjo0tF4IxWlgJNGF%2FdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a70a66cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181227%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59073575&h=9e0a1fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181227&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59073575</a><br />\n<br />\n保加利亞已故失明女預言家萬加（Baba Vanga）再有遺下的預言面世，外國傳媒報道指她預測來年歐洲經濟崩潰，美俄領袖將有劫數，真的信不信由你。<br />\n<br />\n萬加遺下的預言，指美國總統特朗普來年凶險，將患上神秘疾病，導致嘔吐、耳鳴、腦損傷甚至失聰。他一位家人則會捲入車禍。有報道聯想起近年美國駐古巴及廣州的外交人員曾遭神秘聲波襲擊，出現腦損傷、聽力受損、作嘔及頭痛等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n此外，萬加預測俄羅斯總統普京明年將遭其保安團隊一員行刺，大難不死。根據預言，普京亦可能要提防巨型隕石襲擊俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n萬加又預言明年歐洲會出垷經濟崩潰，有傳媒分析相信，若然英國如期明年3月29日脫歐，對歐洲經濟的衝擊難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">萬加預測來年一場大地震及所引發的海嘯將席捲亞洲廣泛地區，巴基斯坦、印度、中國、日本及剛發生海嘯的印尼都會當災。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n有「巴爾幹半島諾查丹馬斯」（Nostradamus of the Balkans）之稱的萬加，12歲時遇到一場暴風後離奇失明，卻得了預知未來及醫治別人的能力。她1996年以85歲高齡逝世，遺下預言「錦囊」一直預測到第51世紀世界末日為止，據說準確度達85%，曾準確預測911恐怖襲擊、南亞大海嘯、英國脫歐、「伊斯蘭國」崛起等。"},{"pid":"b79dece8db08dc20b54ac65e78b8f1954460ce85","tid":957334,"uid":105678,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"個個都話準確預測911<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e84cb696d071c0165b5a1ab12c76583b8eb084","tid":957334,"uid":24730,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"佢知美國總統係侵侵、俄國總統係普京？"},{"pid":"8ff6458227ecf6439bcde29e5e10b6f32b28403c","tid":957334,"uid":55511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"去到51世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁驚乜春"},{"pid":"b3b07d1db829947ce9159175516bf72f9baad333","tid":957334,"uid":136472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda500e45e0e6703e950ffd6bd2f74809049c882","tid":957334,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"我話唐山會再大地震TIM<br />\nUP得就UP"},{"pid":"2fb7d8fab9764e9166314a99e7f30fccd2c8f42e","tid":957334,"uid":224672,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8ff6458227ecf6439bcde29e5e10b6f32b28403c","tid":957334,"uid":55511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"去到51世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁驚乜春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"又可以繼續用飲管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0842e91bfc1a6b7568c9c83f3bd5e07736e9912f","tid":957334,"uid":65346,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"菲律賓大海嘯 99%<br />\n秦國 1%"},{"pid":"df95e81e015794b1bdf03aae45fb26987591585a","tid":957334,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ff98c307da25486286458f73d709862326da8a","tid":957334,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"信佢一成，雙目失明"},{"pid":"37afd38aa9dda05cb29ed4d538b865d98361